Flag to specify soil-water evapotranspiration (ET) computation method. Either it's based on unsatisfied potential ET (PET) and for GSFLOW or GSFLOW5 modes replenish the upper zone of capillary reservoir using the fraction of the upper zone of the capillary reservoir (as was done in previous versions) or it's based on PET when specified equal to 1 and replenish by first filling the lower zone and then the upper zone to their maximum water-holding capactities; set to 0 for downward compatibility of old models, though it is recommended setting to 1 for new models.
